Package: pldist
Title: Paired and Longitudinal Ecological Dissimilarities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Anna M.", "Plantinga", email = "amp9@williams.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Jun", "Chen", role = c("aut")))
Author: Anna M. Plantinga [aut, cre], Jun Chen [aut]
Maintainer: Anna M. Plantinga <amp9@williams.edu>
Description: Calculates paired and longitudinal UniFrac, Bray-Curtis, Jaccard, Gower, and 
    Kulczynski distances/dissimilarities. These metrics summarize changes in the microbiome 
    over time and allow these changes to be compared across treatments, conditions, or 
    levels of a covariate. For more information, please see Plantinga et al (2018+).  
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
Imports: ape
License: GPL-3
